### status: runtime-confirmed,recommended
### public: false
### authRequired: true
### sessionAuthRequired: false
### tenantScopedHeadersRequired: true
### destructive: false
### requiresTenantHeaders: true
### llmOperational: true
### protectedContract: false
### referenceOnly: false
### runtimeRecordConfirmed: true
### selectorConfirmed: true
### publishedBackendConfirmed: true
### knownPublishedFailure: false
### responseShapeHint: page<option>
### selectionGuidance: contract-reference
### note: Demonstrates cascading Entity Lookup with companyId and supplierId dependencies.
### note: ACTIVE/SIGNED contracts return selectable=true; EXPIRED/CANCELLED remain visible with selectable=false.

@baseUrl = https://praxis-api-quickstart.onrender.com
@tenantId = demo
@userId = example-user
@envId = public

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/procurement/contracts/option-sources/contract/options/filter?search=CTR&page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-User-ID: {{userId}}
X-Env: {{envId}}

< ../../payloads/resources/procurement_contract_entity_lookup_filter.json
